# turnip-bot
A discord bot for keeping track of turnip prices for Animal Crossing.

The goal of this was to get a bit more familiar with discord bots, and help some friends coordinate playing Animal Crossing.




Make sure to have ruby installed

To setup:
1. run `gem install bundler`
2. run `bundle install`

To test:
bundle exec ruby main.rb


